legs.end_address: Kefevi, Sinop Arkiyoloji Müzesi, 57000 Sinop Merkez/Sinop, Turkey

steps.html_instructions: Take the ramp to Kocaeli Çayırova Yolu/Kurtuluş Blv.

Continue onto Kocaeli Çayırova Yolu/Kurtuluş Blv.
Continue to follow Kurtuluş Blv.

Keep right at the fork and merge onto Yeni Kandıra Yolu/D605
Continue to follow D605

Turn left onto the ramp to Anadolu Otoyolu/O-4/E80
Partial toll road

Keep right at the fork, follow signs for Sapanca/Ankara/O-4/E80 and merge onto Anadolu Otoyolu/O-4/E80
Toll road

Take the exit toward Gerede-Karabük Bağlantısı/E80
Toll road

Continue onto Gerede-Karabük Bağlantısı/E80
Continue to follow E80
Partial toll road
Continue straight to stay on Boyabat Tosya Yolu/D785

Turn left onto Boyabat Havza Yolu/D030
Continue to follow D030

Merge onto Sinop Bafra Yolu/D010
Continue to follow D010
At the roundabout, continue straight onto Fatih Cd.
Keep right to continue toward Bülent Ecevit Cd.
At Uğur Mumcu Meydanı, take the 4th exit onto Atatürk Cd.
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Derviş Sarabil Cd.
